1 mercantile establishments within a period of 72 hours as part of the same
2 act or transaction or in two or more acts or transactions connected together
3 or constituting parts of a common scheme or course of conduct is a
4 severity level 9, nonperson felony;
5 (6) property of the value of at least $50 but less than $1,500 is a
6 severity level 9, nonperson felony if committed by a person who has,
